## Netcat variants on Ubuntu
-a always,exit -F arch=b64 -F path=/bin/nc.openbsd -F perm=x -k susp_activity
-a always,exit -F arch=b32 -F path=/bin/nc.openbsd -F perm=x -k susp_activity
